cript to ApJ. We find that relative to solar the\nabundances in the Mrk 279 outflow are (linear scaling): carbon 2.2 +/- 0.7,\nnitrogen 3.5 +/- 1.1 and oxygen 1.6 +/- 0.8.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Nov 2006 00:53:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
